置里找功能，想着多年前有用过安卓蓝牙传输，结果不知道为啥两台手机都搜不到对方。在家人的鄙视中，我只能弱弱的来一句，我下个微信。。。。</p>\n","last_modified":1615693659,"replies":40,"id":761471},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1615112532","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1615112532","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":170126,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1615112532","stars":3186,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"wangxiaoaer","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4726a1e637f3210184a90f9a29963a6b?s=24&d=retro","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wangxiaoaer","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1520213711,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4726a1e637f3210184a90f9a29963a6b?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4726a1e637f3210184a90f9a29963a6b?s=24&d=retro","location":"","btc":"","id":296604},"last_reply_by":"oopc","last_touched":1615720023,"title":"软路由","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/761443","created":1615687029,"content":"之前关注过软路由，但是没有跟进，最近又在首页看到几个帖子，心里有点痒，但是有几个问题：\r\n\r\n1 所谓的软路由跟可以刷系统的硬路由有何区别？仅仅是性能吗？\r\n\r\n2 对科学上网的支持有多方便？\r\n\r\n自己用的 AC68U，最初刷的梅林固件，通过插件上网，但是服务商不是非常稳定，切换节点就特别麻烦，通过手机浏览器接入路由器管理页面，特别麻烦（台式机直接网线接入光猫）。软路由这方面配置操作会不会简单点？\r\n\r\n3 硬件\r\n\r\n看了大多的教程，列出 CPU 、内存、SSD 就完事了，留下我一脸懵逼，机箱呢？ 虽说可以用旧机器，但是功耗、稳定性不一定可以啊。难道机箱就是用工控机？ 对这块太不了解了。\r\n\r\n4 必要性\r\n\r\n我没有虚拟化、NAS 等要求，就一个科学上网、去广告等，有没有必要上软路由？\r\n\r\n5 价格：如果需要上，价格大概多少。","content_rendered":"<p>之前关注过软路由，但是没有跟进，最近又在首页看到几个帖子，心里有点痒，但是有几个问题：</p>\n<p>1 所谓的软路由跟可以刷系统的硬路由有何区别？仅仅是性能吗？</p>\n<p>2 对科学上网的支持有多方便？</p>\n<p>自己用的 AC68U，最初刷的梅林固件，通过插件上网，但是服务商不是非常稳定，切换节点就特别麻烦，通过手机浏览器接入路由器管理页面，特别麻烦（台式机直接网线接入光猫）。软路由这方面配置操作会不会简单点？</p>\n<p>3 硬件</p>\n<p>看了大多的教程，列出 CPU 、内存、SSD 就完事了，留下我一脸懵逼，机箱呢？ 虽说可以用旧机器，但是功耗、稳定性不一定可以啊。难道机箱就是用工控机？ 对这块太不了解了。</p>\n<p>4 必要性</p>\n<p>我没有虚拟化、NAS 等要求，就一个科学上网、去广告等，有没有必要上软路由？</p>\n<p>5 价格：如果需要上，价格大概多少。</p>\n","last_modified":1615687029,"replies":39,"id":761443},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1614829351","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1614829351","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":9203,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1614829351","stars":4874,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"suanbaner","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c22e/7625/124107_mini.png?m=1542874354","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/suanbaner","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1435219308,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c22e/7625/124107_mini.png?m=1542874354","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c22e/7625/124107_mini.png?m=1542874354","location":"","btc":"","id":124107},"last_reply_by":"sarices","last_touched":1615717645,"title":"搭了一个测速服务器，欢迎压测，服务器带宽 10G","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/761503","created":1615703658,"content":"http://40.72.115.123:81/","content_rendered":"<p><a href=\"http://40.72.115.123:81/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://40.72.115.123:81/</a></p>\n","last_modified":1615703658,"replies":36,"id":761503},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1615112532","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1615112532","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":170126,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1615112532","stars":3186,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"walkbox","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,