er","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1614829460","stars":7290,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"username":"xuegy","website":"","github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a14fd036007f13550119309d4ee7e0f1?s=24&d=retro","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xuegy","tagline":"","twitter":null,"created":1421601097,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a14fd036007f13550119309d4ee7e0f1?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a14fd036007f13550119309d4ee7e0f1?s=24&d=retro","location":"","btc":null,"id":92500},"last_reply_by":"inhzus","last_touched":1615719407,"title":"从 Linux 换到黑苹果的一些感想","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/761527","created":1615712158,"content":"优点：\r\n\r\n1. 桌面颜值高又稳定\r\n\r\n2. 字体渲染好看，4K 屏效果最好没有之一\r\n\r\n3. 同一张显卡 3D 图形性能原地翻倍\r\n\r\n4. 对蓝牙耳机友好，Linux 的蓝牙和音频都是半残\r\n\r\n\r\n缺点：\r\n\r\n1. 系统自带的包太旧了，装了新的还要避免冲突\r\n\r\n2. Homebrew 的包太新了，大版本一言不合就直接升级\r\n\r\n3. 代码编译选项简直是两个世界\r\n\r\n4. 网上可查资料远少于 Linux\r\n\r\n总的来说，macOS 金玉其外败絮其中。当然 Linux 败絮其外也不是什么值得称赞的事情。终极解决方案可能是把电脑装回 Linux，再买个 Mac mini...","content_rendered":"<p>优点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>桌面颜值高又稳定</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>字体渲染好看，4K 屏效果最好没有之一</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>同一张显卡 3D 图形性能原地翻倍</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>对蓝牙耳机友好，Linux 的蓝牙和音频都是半残</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>缺点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>系统自带的包太旧了，装了新的还要避免冲突</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Homebrew 的包太新了，大版本一言不合就直接升级</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>代码编译选项简直是两个世界</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>网上可查资料远少于 Linux</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>总的来说，macOS 金玉其外败絮其中。当然 Linux 败絮其外也不是什么值得称赞的事情。终极解决方案可能是把电脑装回 Linux，再买个 Mac mini...</p>\n","last_modified":1615712158,"replies":15,"id":761527},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1614829460","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1614829460","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":43750,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas